com.interpss.core.net.childnet

Interface ChildNetInterface

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ChildNetInterfaceBranch, ChildNetInterfaceBus, ChildNetInterfaceBusLoad
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ChildNetInterfaceBranchImpl, ChildNetInterfaceBusImpl, ChildNetInterfaceBusLoadImpl, ChildNetInterfaceImpl

    public interface ChildNetInterface
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Child Net Interface'. Base bus or branch interface for defining parnet-child interface.

    The following features are supported:

    • Parant Child Net Wrapper
    See Also:
